data.description: Perfect opportunity to purchase a duplex in the heart of Deerfield. This duplex has a lot of great features including huge fenced in yard, laminate floors throughout both units, granite countertops, updated bathrooms and kitchen, and newer appliances. This duplex is located just off of Hillsboro only minutes from the beach, shops, restaurants, I95, and more. THIS IS A GREAT OPPORTUNITY!!!!
